                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 33.062,
                                "byte_start": 73687,
                                "byte_stop": 205971,
                                "text": "The judgments and opinions of the Court in three cases: 74-1023, Kerr against the United States District Court; 74-1254, the Oil Chemical and Atomic Workers against Mobile Corporation; and 74-1471, TSC Industries against Northway Incorporated, will each be announced by Mr. Justice Marshall."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 33.062,
                        "stop": 137.679,
                        "byte_start": 205971,
